00:17:32.050 --> 00:17:33.040
than a machine.

00:17:33.040 --> 00:17:35.570
He has a personality, he has
an agenda, and he is one of

00:17:35.570 --> 00:17:36.180
the main characters.

00:17:36.180 --> 00:17:38.090
It was the first time I
saw potentially what a

00:17:38.090 --> 00:17:39.300
machine could be.

00:17:39.300 --> 00:17:42.340
Now, we're not there yet, but
my motivation is R2-D2."

