00:18:43.770 --> 00:18:46.810
know all the ideas and all the
solutions, but he was able to

00:18:46.810 --> 00:18:50.110
go out into his surrounding
force and ask a lot of

00:18:50.110 --> 00:18:51.750
questions, the [INAUDIBLE]
experts.

00:18:51.750 --> 00:18:54.380
And I'm sure each one of you
