The initial technical area or
original concept might be one

00:19:18.340 --> 00:19:21.450
person's contribution, but it'll
need to be reduced to

00:19:21.450 --> 00:19:24.330
practice in the lab, scaled
up, utility-tested and

00:19:24.330 --> 00:19:26.070
vetted."

